OL,5,G0600 Teleshopping
OL,6,G0700 Shop: Must Have Ideas
OL,7,     FDiscover the very latest
OL,8,     Fmust-haves for your home and
OL,9,     Fgarden with Must Have Ideas
OL,10,G0730 eFOLDi Mobility Scooters
OL,11,     FAward winning eFOLDi lightweight
OL,12,     Felectric folding mobility
OL,13,     Fscooters.
OL,14,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,15,     FSeries favourite "Coco" has a new
OL,16,     Frescue - a black stallion he has
OL,17,     Fnamed Black Beauty, who has
OL,18,     Fmedical problems and needs some
OL,19,     Fcareful attention from Colin and
OL,20,     Fhis Spanish vet Antonio.
