OL,5,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,6,     FWe meet again with series
OL,7,     Ffavourite Colin "Coco" Brown, who
OL,8,     Fwe usually see working hard at the
OL,9,     Fanimal rescue centre and farm he
OL,10,     Fruns with his partner Sebastian
OL,11,     Fand son Hugo.
OL,12,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,13,     FCatching up with the victims and
OL,14,     Fvillains of the rental market.
OL,15,     FRachel intended to rent out her
OL,16,     Fcottage for three months; four
OL,17,     Fyears later, her tenant is still
OL,18,     Fthere.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
