OL,5,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FIn North Yorkshire, cops are out
OL,7,     Fin force, protecting lorry drivers
OL,8,     Fand their cargo as organised gangs
OL,9,     Ftarget goods and trucks. Ther's a
OL,10,     Fhijack on an HGV carrying
OL,11,     F#1million of goods.
OL,12,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FOn a busy Bank Holiday weekend, a
OL,14,     Fday trip to Scarborough turns into
OL,15,     Fa high-speed pursuit and a
OL,16,     Fdesperate suspect on a motorbike
OL,17,     Fputs lives at risk when a
OL,18,     Fpassenger falls off.
