OL,5,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FDoors get smashed in dawn raids on
OL,7,     Fdrug dealers, shots are fired in a
OL,8,     Fsuburban siege, and bad guys are
OL,9,     Fchased at more than 100mph.
OL,10,G1700 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,11,     FUndercover detective Steve tails
OL,12,     Ftwo suspects who previously evaded
OL,13,     Fcapture, and later deals with a
OL,14,     Fwoman suspected of stealing
OL,15,     Fthousands of pounds' worth of
OL,16,     Fperfume. (Ep3)
OL,17,G1800 Home and Away
OL,18,     FCash and Eden find a compromise.
OL,19,     FMackenzie breaks down. Mali tricks
OL,20,     FJohn.
