OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FMackenzie and Levi struggle to
OL,7,     Fprocess their grief. Lacey worries
OL,8,     Ffor her dad. Richie visits David.
OL,9,G1900 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,10,     FIt's a busy night at Barnsley
OL,11,     FHopsital's casualty department, so
OL,12,     Fwhen Sister Benita arrives to head
OL,13,     Fthe shift, the corridors are
OL,14,     Falready packed full of patients.
OL,15,G2000 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,16,     FIn Birmingham, Jane is fed up with
OL,17,     Fa painful rash on her scalp;
OL,18,     FMyfanwy has concerns that her mum
OL,19,     Fmay have sepsis after a procedure;
OL,20,     Fand Jean discusses her mental
OL,21,     Fhealth struggles.
